snippet.title: The Delusions of Maximillian Wurst - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The first chapter of a loop-de-loop platformer in which you control Maximillian Wurst, silver-tongued poet and abject moron, as he pursues a fantasy that wants nothing to do with him. Escape Father Time! Shoot as many Chadwicks as you can! Stumble along with poison coursing through your lily liver! 

Music composed by Elizabeth Legierski.

Wishlist the demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1951350

https://www.deadpancancan.com/
